snippet.title: Mob Factory Trailer [January 2023]
snippet.description:
Wishlist at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2182630/Mob_Factory

Watch the new trailer at: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lZtWl7LqfAM

Mob factory is an automation game where the enemies are the inputs. The game is releasing Q1 of 2023 for the PC.
